    dc:title "New and little-known species of Meligethes Stephens, 1830 from China (Coleoptera: Nitidulidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5174106>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5174110>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5174112> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5174106>
    dc:description "Figs. 1-12. Tegmen and aedeagus (dorsal aspect) of Meligethes Stephens, 1830. 1-2 – M. difficiloides sp. nov., J paratype from Yunnan, Weibao Mts. 3-4 – M. dieckmanni Audisio & Jelínek, 1984, J from Turkey, Kars province, Göle. 5-6 – M. difficilis (Heer, 1841), J from Italy, Rome. 7-8 – M. atrovirens Jelínek, 1982, J from Turkey, Giresun province, Kümbet. 9-10 – M. abditus sp. nov., J paratype from Beijing principality, Xiaolongmen. 11-12 – M. chlorocupreus sp. nov., J paratype from Yunnan, Weibao Mts. Scale bar = 0.20 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5174106/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5174110>
    dc:description "Figs. 20-23. Right front tibiae of Meligethes Stephens, 1830. 20 – M. difficiloides sp. nov., J paratype from Yunnan, Weibao Mts.; 21 – M. abditus sp. nov., J holotype from Beijing principality, Xiaolongmen; 22 – M. chlorocupreus sp. nov., J paratype from Yunnan, Weibao Mts.; 23 – M. bocaki sp. nov., J paratype from Yunnan, Luo Shui (23). Scale bar = 0.20 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5174110/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5174112>
    dc:description "Figs. 24-27. Body outlines of Meligethes Stephens, 1830. 24 – M. difficiloides sp. nov., J paratype from Yunnan, Weibao Mts.; 25 – M. abditus sp. nov., J holotype from Beijing principality, Xiaolongmen; 26 – M. chlorocupreus sp. nov., J holotype from Yunnan, Weibao Mts.; 27 – M. bocaki sp. nov., J paratype from Yunnan, Luo Shui. Scale bar = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5174112/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

